title: 2 + 5 | What is 2 plus 5?
text: Addition: 2 + 5 The sum of two plus five is equal to seven. We can also express that 2 plus 5 equals 7 as follows: 2 + 5 = 7 2 plus 5 = 7 What is 2 plus by other numbers? - 2 plus 6 = 8 - 2 plus 7 = 9 - 2 plus 8 = 10 - 2 plus 9 = 11 - 2 plus 10 = 12 - 2 plus 11 = 13 - 2 plus 12 = 14 - 2 plus 13 = 15 - 2 plus 14 = 16 - 2 plus 15 = 17
